<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>291</hymn_number>
<title>GO AND WORK</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kristien tho un ip ta kiu,
 Kapte I chawlhsan mai dem?
 Lalpan thu ei piek lai hin,
 Mawk chut mai mai ding I him?

[V2]
 Chieh un, sem un, tun pan un,
 Chieh un hawl un beimangte;
 Gitloh thim laka chengte,
 Hinna An um di'n sam un!

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa I lungsiet um?
 A thupiek I zui ding um?
 I neih cheng I piephal dem?
 Ei sapna awn I nung dem?

[V4]
 3. I gin ding bangun I gingum?
 Ei hilh bangin I um um?
 Amah mai a I hiu em?
 Ginna nasep in phuong hen.

[V5]
 4. Kross I put dinguh a um,
 Lallukhuk neih I guot chun;
 Thanuom takin pang hitiu,
 Phat a chawm, ni a tawm tai.</lyrics>
</song>